Services

Class NotificationService

  • java.lang.Object
    • Services.NotificationService

  • public class NotificationService
extends java.lang.Object
    NotificationService.java is the Service class used to perform all the business operations on notification objects, such as retrieving, creating, modifying and deleting notifications.
